    "description": "An exciting career opportunity awaits you at Licious Consulting Pvt Ltd. We are on the lookout for a dedicated Digital Marketing Manager to strengthen our Ahmedabad-based team.\n\nAbout Licious Consulting Pvt Ltd:\nLicious Consulting Pvt Ltd is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Monitor and improve Net Promoter Score (NPS) and customer satisfaction\n• Manage marketplace relationships with Amazon, Flipkart, and Meesho\n• Create engaging content for product pages and social media\n• Execute digital marketing campaigns across Google, Meta, and other channels\n• Conduct competitor analysis and market benchmarking\n• Analyze sales data and customer behavior to drive revenue growth\n• Manage product listings, pricing, and promotions on the platform\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Tech / B.E. in Computer Science or related discipline\n• 10-15 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Digital Marketing\n• Proficiency in Affiliate Marketing\n• Proficiency in A/B Testing\n• Proficiency in Content Writing\n• Proficiency in Facebook Ads\n• Proficiency in Retention Marketing\n• Proficiency in Performance Marketing\n• Proficiency in Customer Segmentation\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Flexible working hours\n• Salary Range: 20 LPA - 40 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Ahmedabad, Gujarat, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Licious Consulting Pvt Ltd!",
